review_title: Quality product. Very simple - select ear buds from bluetooth list and you are set.
reviews: These are quality ear buds with rich sound and a nice storage/charging case. I am a Luddite and the set up takes 10 seconds. Just select from list of bluetooth devices and you are set. You do have to disconnect before switching to another device. Very pleased.
This is a well made hat. Looks good.
This is a proper fitted hat. Very pleased.

These would be a great bargain if they worked. They don't. We had the basic indoor RCA flat panel that worked well enough. It picked up 12 channels in our location - sometimes more. This one picked up just one local channel but not well, even though that transmitter is only about 8 km away with only Lake Ontario between.

Based on prior reviews I was expecting better quality and weight. They are just okay. They feel light and not particularly well made for a medium priced set of knives. The magnetic "block" was decent quality but not of any use if you don't want to display your knives on the counter.

We bought four "bed in a box" mattresses for a small summer home in Newfoundland. We could not fit regular box spring type mattresses up the stairs. Free shipping to the very rural door was a big bonus. We are pleased with them all but these two are the most comfortable (medium firm), and had the best quality cover. In my experience, they are every bit as good quality and comfortable as mattresses from major brand names costing three times as much. No off-gassing issues. A great bargain.
You will be amazed at how sharp this knife is and how easily and cleanly it cuts bread, cake and tomatoes. It is the America Test Kitchen winner and you will understand why.
Great quality and very sharp. Good value for the money.

These are fantastic quality lenses for the price. A dramatic improvement over what I had. Wide field of view. For me, these are about as powerful as can be hand held without mounting them on a tripod. Great for spotting whales, other wildlife, boats and shoreline.

review_title: Smaller than it appears in the photos. Wrong mount.
reviews: This unit is much smaller and lighter than I was expecting. The mounting bracket makes it unsuitable for use in a normal sized shower stall as it does not permit enough adjustment to direct the spray down rather that horizontally. The most downward adjustment still has the water spraying directly at the shower door. I tried it in three shower stalls and had to remove it each time due to the adjustment problem. I delayed installing it and the return window expired.

review_title: Smaller and heavier than you may think
reviews: I bought these for children to play dress-up. They use them, but it is a delicate exercise to keep them on their head. It is very heavy and smaller in circumference than you may be thinking. This one sits on top of the head, not around it like a hat. It requires bobby pins to hold it on and it falls off easily. i think it is intended for fancy hairdos more suitable for a bride at a wedding. Even then, it is so heavy, that it would come flying off with any sudden movement. Decent quality for the price. They seem unnecessarily chunky and heavy. This one was the lightest and most attractive of the three I bought and could be adjusted somewhat.

They seem unnecessarily chunky and heavy. This one was the least attractive of the three I bought.

review_title: Works well - but not on Champagne bottles
reviews: These work well on wine bottles but do not fit on Champagne bottles. Good quality.

This is the second bluetooth transmitter I got for a second TV. This one was much more compact and genuinely was plug and play. It paired right away without having to read directions. There is not perceptible delay in the audio. It is probably just a setting on the TV and the fact that I am using the earphone jack, but plugging this one in causes the TV speakers to mute. It has an annoying flashing light that activates when the tv and headphones are turned off. That is annoying when using it in a dark bedroom and you want to sleep. The flashing light does stop after a few minutes.

Decent quality and weight, but smallish for my largish head. I bought 4 different toques at the same time and this one is not as soft or stretchy as the similar Carhart brand I got. It is made in the USA which is nice.

review_title: The best of the four I bought
reviews: I bought four toques at the same time, adding to several I already had. I like this one the best. It is the softest and has a gentle stretch so it never feels tight. It fits well. It is warm without becoming too hot. The black one I got is made in Canada and is the best quality of them all.

We use these for cafe latte made directly into them on a super automatic espresso maker. We first steam the milk directly into the cup, then add two shots of espresso directly into the same cup. I get a bit of joy every time watching the physics of two unlike fluids mixing and settling. We have had them for a couple of months and put them in the dishwasher without issue. Just be careful not to place other items that can move in contact with them. The only drawback is that I usually gauge the milk temperature but feeling the warmth coming through the cup. That does not work on these insulated cups so now I have to time the steaming of the milk.

review_title: Consistent quality for mild/meduim roast coffee
reviews: We have had a super automatic espresso machine for about 10 years now and have tried several brands and roasts of coffee. We are making large cappuccinos or small cafe lattes. This makes a full bodied but mild cup of coffee. It never bridges in the coffee hopper. It compares well with local high end fresh roasted coffee.

Fits well and good quality. The drain hole is about 1/2 inch off for our sink but that is not an issue other than minor estetic. Make sure you measure where your drain is. If you want a close fit, measure your sink 1 inch up from the bottom as this drain rests on feet that are 1 inch high

This cover is of good heavy duty quality and fits well except it is six inches too short, leaving the base and bottom four inches of the cabinet exposed. This is a brand name Charbroil cover on a Charbroil two burner bbq - the same bbq as shown on the package the cover came in. As many have already mentioned, the velcro fasteners are only two inch tabs that are totally useless - but the cover fits well and is heavy gauge enough that they are not really necessary anyway.
